body: I'm not sure I am thinking about this correctly. I've noticed from a previous issue that I posted (https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/issues/2516) that the numerical and theoretical gradients provided by `tf.test.compute_gradient_error` should not be the same in the case of complex ops.
